INTRODUCTION :
          Billing System Project is a simple console application designed to demonstrate the practical use of C programming language 
and its features as wells as to generate an application which can be used in any departmental store, shops, cafes etc. for billing to the customer.
You can use this application to keep the records such as name, address, mobile number, paid amount, due amount, payment date etc. of your regular costumer. 
Moreover, if you have a new customer, you can add and edit the account at any time.The source code of Billing System Project in C has been written in 
C programming language without of the use of any graphics. Although graphics has not been used in this project, 
the application of user defined functions and structures have been effectively used here. 

Defining our system :

User can add the new customer account and the parameters such as name, address, phone number, amount paid etc. are asked and entered. 
and these infoemation are stored on hard disc of computer by the files created.
And there is a provision to look for previously stored accounts either by name or by number of the customer.

SWOT analysis :

Strength - customizable and easy to use 
Weakness - chances of getting outdated
Opportunity - collaboration and adaptable for various types of system
Threats - there is less chances for threats

4W's and 1H :

WHO - it is created for the user to easy handle of the bill records
WHAT - this system is for registering the purchase records of the customers
WHERE - it is very useful in shops and stores
WHEN - it is solution for the challanges faced during manual billing 

HOW - it is being done using some functions and files in the C programming language 


High level requirements:

a)item details
b)item costs
c)customer details

Low level requirements:

a)quantity of the items 
b)total cost of the items
c)Gst,discounts,offers
d)additon operator
e)subtraction operator
